    About the Business

    Business owner information

    Omer Y.

    Business Owner

    Om's Remodeling is a leading home remodeling, kitchen remodeling and bathroom remodeling company in San Mateo ,CA and the Bay Area, that specializes in all your home remodeling, construction and renovation needs, including: Kitchen remodeling / kitchen renovating : our kitchen remodeling team offers a wide selection of kitchen cabinets, kitchen countertops and modern kitchen flooring that can suit any project. Bathroom remodeling / bathroom renovating : our bathroom remodeling designers offer a wide selection of bathroom vanities, bathtubs, standing showers and bathroom flooring that can compliment any bathroom remodeling project. Home remodeling: Our home remodeling services also include: backyard remodeling, room additions, foundation services. Additional services: Flooring : we offer tile floor installation: ceramic flooring, granite flooring, porcelain flooring, woodgrain flooring, vinyl flooring and more. Hardwood floor installation including all types of hardwood. We offer all types of general construction projects for both residential and commercial property owners.…

      Had a great "remodel" experience with Om's!

      Dan came over to discuss our bathroom remodel - he listened, was courteous, gave us many options - gave us a quote and timeline for the project.  We found Om's to be slightly on the pricier side, but we would hire them again in a heartbeat!  Worth every penny!

      Dan showed up on a regular basis to make sure all was on track, and was available any time we had a question/concern.  He walks with you through the whole project and is in constant communication.  

      Included with the cost is a designer to help everything come together - Supriya met me at the store to put all the tiles together - she then gives you a 3D version photo, with the tiles you select so you can see what your bathroom will look like before proceeding - super cool. She would also approve any purchases to ensure everything would fit properly (vanity, mirror, toilet, shower fixtures).  Was very comforting to have someone available to assure that all your purchases would work out.

      Dan's team was great - Alberto knows his stuff - if you have the luck of Alberto being on your project, take his advice and recommendations - he knows what he's doing!  Guys were very polite - very respectful of your privacy and cleaned up every day.

      They finished on time, and we were so pleased that the project cost exactly what Dan quoted.

      Look forward to working with them again on our next project!

      I wish I could give more than 5 stars because this team is the absolute best.  We had met with 3 other contractors before choosing Daniel and the team at Om's and I'm so, so glad we found these guys.  

      We had originally hired them to help us with a bathroom remodel and kitchen upgrade and ended up having them upgrade all of our light fixtures and full home electrical as well as exterior paint in full because we loved working with them so much.  We'll be having them back for a master bedroom update in the future too!

      From start to finish the experience was amazing.  Our vision was executed in full with so many incredible details that came as a complete bonus.  What I loved was that Daniel always listened to our concepts but would offer other options that could improve the end result.  Most of the times we agreed and his suggestions improved our project greatly, but if we ever didn't want to move forward with something he was never pushy either.

      We had David and his team here on the day to day interior demo and finishing work and working with truly every single person we met was incredible.  The attention to detail, kindness, cleanliness, respect of budget and everything else surpassed our expectations.

      We contacted six companies looking for one that could do a partial remodel of our guest bathroom including new flooring, vanity, sink, lighting, toilet, ventilation fan, outlets, and shower/tub faucets.  The only thing we did not remodel was the tile surrounding the bathtub.  Some companies were extremely difficult to deal with and wouldn't even consider anything that was not a complete remodeling project.  We are so glad that one of the companies we initially contacted was OMS Remodeling.  Even before we knew some of the other companies would decline a partial project, thus ruling them out from the decision, we had already rated OMS Remodeling as one of the top contenders for the project based on their initial responsiveness, thoroughness, and professionalism.    

      Yuval was the project manager for our bathroom remodeling project.  He was professional and readily available to help with any questions or concerns we had along the way.  We were impressed with Yuval from our very first meeting.  He was one of the few company representatives that actually sat down and went over all aspects of the project in detail at the first meeting, focusing on what it is that you want, but adding his recommendations where appropriate. Even when we ran into an unexpected problem, Yuval considered the issue and offered an efficient method for resolving the problem.  The hardworking crew that came out to work on the project was equally impressive, completing the project in a very timely manner, without losing their attention to detail. The results are fantastic and the bathroom looks amazing.

       Whether you have a large or a small project, OMS Remodeling is willing to assist you and will provide you with excellent service and results.   We highly recommend OMS Remodeling and will use them again in the future.
